milestones.description: Morris Ouma and Alex Obanda's 104-run partnership is KENYA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 100 between Steve Tikolo and Ravi Shah
Lionel Cann has become the top scorer for BMUDA in ODIs with 543 runs, going past Romaine's 535
